---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Our Mission"
  description="The Earthing Institute is a 501(c)(3) nonprofit advancing research on how physical connection with the Earth influences inflammation, nervous system regulation, and human health."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-green-primary py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-6">
        Our Vision & Mission
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/80 font-heading italic max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        A New Health and Healing Frontier
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission Statement -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-12 shadow-sm border border-cream-dark mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-green-primary mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed mb-6">
          The Earthing Institute is a nonprofit research and education organization focused on
          understanding how direct physical connection with the Earth influences inflammation,
          nervous system regulation, and human health.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Chronic inflammation underlies many of today's most costly and debilitating conditions.
          Over more than two decades, peer-reviewed research has explored grounding as a low-cost,
          non-invasive intervention with measurable physiological effects.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed">
          The Institute exists to advance rigorous research, curate credible scientific findings,
          and responsibly educate the public and health professionals worldwide.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-light/50 rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-12 border border-green-primary/10 mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-green-primary mb-6">Our Vision</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed mb-6">
          We envision the day when every human being (and pet) on this planet will be earthed
          throughout their daily life. When that day comes, it will be common knowledge that
          earthing is as important for health as good nutrition, sleep, exercise, and a positive
          mental attitude.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed">
          Our mission is to disseminate this vital knowledge to as many people as we can throughout
          the world. We want to further research regarding the health benefits of earthing, and to
          have our website serve as a repository of all information related to earthing.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- President's Message -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-12 shadow-sm border border-cream-dark mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-green-primary mb-8">
          A Message from Our President
        </h2>
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8">
          <div class="shrink-0">
            <div class="w-40 h-40 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-green-light to-cream-dark flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-green-primary/10 mx-auto flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-green-primary/40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                    <path d="M12 12c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm0 2c-2.67 0-8 1.34-8 4v2h16v-2c0-2.66-5.33-4-8-4z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <p class="text-xs text-green-primary/50 mt-2">Photo</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed mb-4">
              As a researcher involved primarily with the physics of electricity and the body's
              electrophysiology (how the body produces and utilizes electrical energy), I find it
              amazing that at this point in the human timeline we are just exploring the Earth as
              a resource for health and healing.
            </p>
            <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Past cultures put great emphasis on connectedness with the Earth, a relationship still
              honored by many indigenous people today. To what extent this connection was recognized
              as a healing factor among past cultures is not a subject that has been studied. Now,
              finally, science is exploring the dynamics and benefits of this connection.
            </p>
            <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed mb-4">
              The studies I have been involved with have painted an intriguing picture of what happens
              when we connect to the Earth. In short, it is as if a switch has been turned on, and,
              in response, the body's inner workings start functioning more efficiently and robustly.
            </p>
            <p class="font-heading font-bold text-green-primary mt-6">
              Gaetan Chevalier, Ph.D.
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-light">
              President, The Earthing Institute<br />
              Director since 2009
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Board of Directors -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-green-primary mb-4">
          Board of Directors
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
        {[
          {
            name: 'Gaetan Chevalier, Ph.D.',
            role: 'President',
            bio: '45-year career in engineering physics, biophysics, and electrophysiology. Director of the Earthing Institute since 2009.',
          },
          {
            name: 'Dr. Katerina Brzovic',
            role: 'Treasurer',
            bio: 'Chilean veterinarian and acupuncturist. Founder of Contacto Tierra, leading earthing education across Latin America and Spain.',
          },
          {
            name: 'Dr. Richard Kotz',
            role: 'CFO',
            bio: 'Retired FDA statistician with 25 years of service reviewing clinical trials for medical devices. FDA Lifetime Achievement Award 2016.',
          },
        ].map(member => (
          <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-6 text-center border border-cream-dark">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-green-light mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-green-primary/30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                <path d="M12 12c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm0 2c-2.67 0-8 1.34-8 4v2h16v-2c0-2.66-5.33-4-8-4z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-heading font-bold text-green-primary mb-1">{member.name}</h3>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-light mb-3">{member.role}</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate leading-relaxed">{member.bio}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <!-- Scientific Advisors -->
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-green-primary mb-4">
          Scientific Advisory Board
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        {[
          { name: 'James Oschman, Ph.D.', role: 'Nature\'s Own Research Association' },
          { name: 'Tracy Latz, M.D., M.S.', role: 'Integrative Psychiatrist' },
          { name: 'Pawel Sokal, M.D., Ph.D.', role: 'Neurosurgeon, Earthing Research Pioneer' },
          { name: 'Tina Michaud-Gray, RN, LMT', role: 'Pain & Soft Tissue Specialist' },
          { name: 'Charles Munier, D.M.D.', role: 'Retired Dentist, TMJ Treatment' },
          { name: 'Jeffrey Spencer, M.A., D.C.', role: 'Former Olympic Cyclist, Tour de France Team' },
        ].map(advisor => (
          <div class="bg-cream rounded-xl p-4 border border-cream-dark">
            <p class="font-semibold text-slate-dark text-sm">{advisor.name}</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-light">{advisor.role}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <!-- In Memoriam -->
      <div class="mt-16 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-green-primary mb-8">In Memoriam</h2>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          {[
            { name: 'Martin Zucker', years: '1937-2020', role: 'Co-author of the Earthing book' },
            { name: 'Stephen Sinatra, M.D.', years: '1946-2022', role: 'Integrative cardiologist, discovered earthing as anti-inflammatory' },
            { name: 'Karol Sokal, M.D., Ph.D.', years: '1944-2023', role: 'Pioneer of earthing research since 1989' },
          ].map(person => (
            <div class="p-6">
              <p class="font-heading font-bold text-slate-dark">{person.name}</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-light">{person.years}</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate mt-2">{person.role}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-green-primary">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-4">
        Support Our Mission
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/80 mb-8">
        Help us advance the science of grounding and bring this vital knowledge to the world.
      </p>
      <a
        href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}donate`}
        class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3.5 bg-white text-green-primary font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-white/90 transition-colors shadow-lg"
      >
        Make a Tax-Deductible Donation
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
          <path d="M3.172 5.172a4 4 0 015.656 0L10 6.343l1.172-1.171a4 4 0 115.656 5.656L10 17.657l-6.828-6.829a4 4 0 010-5.656z" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
